hackathon-rules: The rules of our Hackathon are included in the waiver that must be signed in order to come to HackUC. Click the link in the registration information to learn more.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Win an Apple Series 2 Smartwatch and $50 in gift cards for each member of your team!
Win a Razer Black Widow keyboard and a $25 Chick-fil-A Gift Card for each member of your team!
Win a $35 Amazon Gift Card for each member of your team!
Amazon gift cards worth a total of $40 per team will be disbursed to three teams who did not win one of the three major prizes, but whose projects were still worthy of an honorable mention.
Create an ARK.io related project by learning about ARK through workshops and mentors at the hackathon. Win up $250-$500 in ARK Cryptocurrency!
The team that creates the best project with a .Tech domain wins a $250 Amazon gift card!
Hackers that develop the project most likely to succeed as a startup each receives a Syma X5C 2.4G 6-Axis Gyro RC Quadcopter Drone.
Winners who show the most development from little knowledge will each receive $2000 Makeschool scholarships.
